{"tid":559907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蔡志明頭痕】ICAC與SFC齊上門查康健辦公室","createTime":"2018-02-13T15:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T01:15:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3248760984a7423cc05a322e9fb7efdc7923ddeb","tid":559907,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180213/large/1518524057_0eb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180213%2Flarge%2F1518524057_0eb6.jpg&h=a2a6db53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年11月底開始被證監會勒令停牌的康健國際(3886)發出通告表示，上周五(2月9日)廉政公署與證監會人員，齊到該公司位於沙田小瀝源的寫字樓，執行一項搜查令。<br />\n<br />\n廉署人員就公司涉及《防止賄賂條例》（香港法例第201章）第9(1)及9(2)條項下的指稱罪行，而證監會人員就涉及《證券及期貨條例》（香港法例第571章）第179(1)條，齊到場執行一項搜查令。<br />\n<br />\n董事所深知、盡悉及確信，以上搜查並未影響本集團的業務和營運。<br />\n<br />\n康健國際副主席是「玩具大王」蔡志明，他女兒擔任主席，蔡志明與有「殼股玩家」之稱的曹貴子共同持有康健18.28%。"},{"pid":"4d156df4db82919af1254f3668ae309e5d0aaf63","tid":559907,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"成功需父幹"},{"pid":"dd3a86e1c7a94cc9a67a9cd67b4de02e2a2948d2","tid":559907,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"父幹沒有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffb0ea23611f996d970c327294cbea65be382c1","tid":559907,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"蔡加怡以前好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48615ca78e4a99451baf38832ab50f0da36c4a64","tid":559907,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"醫生單野燒到玩具大王到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b54b600f6ddf3cde6a90fb1bdf4a5a811f11a47","tid":559907,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T01:15:4